Jab Lambda Expression sirf kisi existing method ko call kar rahi ho, tab hum Lambda ki jagah Method Reference :: use kar sakte hain.

1. Static Method
   ClassName::methodName

   Math::sqrt


2. Particular Object ka Instance Method
   object::methodName

   System.out::println


3. Type ka Instance Method
   ClassName::instanceMethod

   String::toUpperCase


4. Constructor Reference
   ClassName::new

   User::new